FBIS3-56224 "drsov010_g_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Defense Minister Meets Polish Counterpart in Grodno LD1401013694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1712 GMT 13 Jan 94 LD1401013694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By BELINFORM correspondent for TASS] [Text] Grodno, 13 Jan--An official meeting between Belarusian Defense Minister Pavel Kozlovskiy and Polish Defense Minister Reserve Vice Admiral Piotr Kolodziejczyk took place here today. This is the first meeting attended by Kolodziejczyk, who was appointed recently to the post of head of Poland's military department. On the agenda were consultations on matters of military organizational development and cooperation in the area of defense between the two states and also on agreeing upon the forms of interaction between the military ministries in the realization of commitments entered into by the sides during the signing of the corresponding bilateral agreements in April 1993. Questions concerning the preservation of peace and security in Europe were also touched upon.
